| Command  | Description                | Example                          |
| -------- | -------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| `tar`    | Create/extract tar archive | `tar -cvf backup.tar /home/user` |
| `gzip`   | Compress files             | `gzip file.txt`                  |
| `gunzip` | Decompress                 | `gunzip file.txt.gz`             |
| `zip`    | Zip files                  | `zip files.zip *.txt`            |
| `unzip`  | Unzip files                | `unzip files.zip`                |
